description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 45, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 90, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 8 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90452-71482-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [90 Votes, Common]
